summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 220E, Page 6 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Block 52, H.E. Orr Park Division No. 5 from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
